docs.title: Making Your First Request
docs.text:
• Example of a basic API request to retrieve all users

    bash curl -X GET "http://158.160.86.46/api/prod/users" -H "Authorization: Token YOUR_API_KEY" -

Example response for successful request:

[
    {
        "id": 123,
        "username": "newUser",
        "email": "user@example.com",
        "firstName": "Имя",
        "lastName": "Фамилия",
        "city": "Город",
        "age": 30
    },
    {
        "id": 124,
        "username": "anotherUser",
        "email": "anotheruser@example.com",
        "firstName": "Another",
        "lastName": "User",
        "city": "City",
        "age": 25
    },
    ...
]
